Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.13,0:21:58.62,EDCN-CHT,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be6}連珍藏的昨日也值得愛憐
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.82,0:22:01.72,EDCN-CHT,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be6}交疊的旋律
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.72,0:22:03.99,EDCN-CHT,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be6}直到明天  直到永遠
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.99,0:22:12.88,EDCN-CHT,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be6}天空見證著我們的祈福
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.81,0:22:19.32,EDCN-CHT,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be6}只因聽見了你的聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.55,0:22:25.10,EDCN-CHT,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be6}我的歌聲便是回應
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.28,0:22:28.15,EDCN-CHT,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be6}無論何時  你我並肩
